.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/T%C3%B4-V%C5%A9-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-TfRPhlA8ANmkI18Fqp1MRw">Tô Vũ miếu - 蘇武廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Qu%C3%A2n/author-VkIfi7DKP2f1cM8JZZP8yA">Ôn Đình Quân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n/T%E1%BB%91ng-Th%C3%B4i-Dung/poem-W2dV40e1DaAHSG4AiMilSw">Tống Thôi Dung - 送崔融</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Th%E1%BA%A9m-Ng%C3%B4n/author-m8VtavBW4Ya78m3-y_Q_Gw">Đỗ Thẩm Ngôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/Truy-ho%E1%BA%A1-T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Xu%C3%A2n-khu%C3%AA/poem-s_PwfmSmPRuJmFYF3Thx_w">Truy hoạ Tùng Thiện Vương “Xuân khuê” - 追和從善王春閨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%A2n/author-IGETeQBwf_c0CasyF8dTBQ">Trần Đình Tân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-ZwfHcB2wHgyGr6GaVQjZsg">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-pJBwoRHVKJ-XuTxRTje2pQ">Chu Nguyên Chương</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
